{
  "texts": [
    "Each question was posed five times in this study.",
    "Hoang et al.",
    "22 investigated the consistency of ChatGPT-3.5 and ChatGPT-4 in providing the energy and macronutrient content of 222 food items across five repeated measurements.",
    "A high number of repeated measurements increases the reliability of evaluations.",
    "However, it also significantly increases the costs and latency of response collection, particularly for techniques such as the CoT-SC, which includes multiple multi-step reasoning paths, and retrieval-augmented prompting."
  ]
}